{"tid":1703423,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同樣都係家長同小朋友，分別大撚到","createTime":"2019-11-10T09:20:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T09:20:36.000Z","uid":325549,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f21c62d372d73ba56427782c027c953531354bd2","tid":1703423,"uid":325549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T09:20:36.000Z","msg":"今日周圍開花<br />\n周圍都係green object 然後片入邊嘅細路同佢老竇展開以下熱烈討論：<br />\n「打爛晒啲地鐵😠」<br />\n「我唔支持普通警察但係我好支持防暴！」<br />\n「遲啲香港就會比警察包圍晒㗎啦☺️」<br />\n「捉曱甴！」<br />\n「嘩好型呀！係全副裝甲！」<br />\nBlablabla......太難聽已不能盡錄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://vimeo.com/372172721\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvimeo.com%2F372172721&d=Fs4PzESj5DMZecC7Kr%2FqWDKIKeATNbIGZROv3ilSK6E%3D&h=359d3c58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://vimeo.com/372172721</a><br />\n<br />\n但係同時，前佢幾個位嘅媽媽就同仔仔睇緊直播<br />\n媽媽一路睇就一路係咁屌鳩班克警，「痴撚線、冇良知、死黑警」<br />\n仔仔好驚咁不停話「我會唔會俾警察拉㗎？🥺」<br />\n聽到我心都痛埋。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">總結：文宣同教育真係好撚重要</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命<br />\n五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可<br />\n11.11 大三罷！</span></strong></span>"}]}